Text: OnePass Offers Spring Reward SaleMore For Your Miles With The Spring Reward Sale Save off the mileage usually required for travel to select destinations in Europe the Caribbean Brazil Mexico and Central America Shop in Frankfurt relax on the beach in Rio de Janeiro or explore the volcanoes of Nicaragua See the chart at wwwonepasscom for available destinations and the mileage required to book your Spring Reward Sale tickets Turn Your Miles into Money and Shop Online Through MilePointcom Register now and earn a free enrollment bonus good for a magazine subscription Registration is free and simple Upon enrollment your MilePoint account will be credited entitling you to choose any one of over titles no cash or credit card payment will be required For complete details and to register click here wwwmilepointcomindexasppcoteam Unfortunately mail sent to this address cannot be answered Please direct all inquiries to Note To modify your OnePass email preferences please login to Your Account at wwwonepasscomyouraccount To unsubscribe from all OnePass partner email programs please visit wwwonepasscomemailpartoffers IMAGE
